OL,3,CGuernsey law updated to include new,
OL,4,Cspecific offence for domestic abuse
OL,6,FGuernsey's States Assembly have
OL,7,Funanimously approved a new, specific
OL,8,Foffence for domestic abuse.
OL,10,FThe legislation is being brought in to
OL,11,F"provide robust protection and justice
OL,12,Ffor victims", and was based on
OL,13,FScottish laws introduced in 2019 which
OL,14,F"better reflect victims' accounts and
OL,15,Fexperiences".
OL,17,FDeputy Rob Prow, President of the Home
OL,18,FAffairs Committee, said "I am
OL,19,Foptimistic it will make a serious
OL,20,Fdifference in the way these offences
OL,21,Fare handled".
